Barplot GSEA output

msigdb_gsea.Rd

Barplot GSEA output

msigdb_gsea(ind, PCAmodel, category = "C2", n = 10, pvalueCutoff = 0.5)

Arguments

ind

An interger. Index of avgLoading/PCcluster to apply GSEA.
PCAmodel

PCAGenomicSignature object.
category

A character vector representing MSigDB category. Options are "H","C1","C2"(default), "C3","C4","C5","C6", and "C7"
n

An interger. The number of top and bottom enriched pathways to plot. Default is 10.
pvalueCutoff

Cutoff for both pvalue and p.adjust. Default is 0.5.

Value

Barplot of GSEA output. Top and bottom n genesets based on NES are plotted and qvalues are denoted by color.
